text: Lea Bachelier (born 13 February 1993) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == *lea-bachelier france-waterpolo *lea-bachelier-of- france getty *lea-bachelier globalsportsarchive Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players Category:People from Nancy Category:Sportspeople from Grand Est
